\c 21
\s Jobho anoti, vakaipa vanenge vanofara havo vasingatambudzwi naMwari, asi vachatongwa panguva inouya
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapindura ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Inzwai muteerere shoko rangu; uye iyi ngaive nyaradzo dzenyu\x + 13.17.\x*.
\v 3 Ndiitirei moyo murefu, ini nditaure; zvino shure kweizvozvo ndataura, mungatuka\x + 16.10,20. 17.2.\x*.
\v 4 Ini, kunyunyuta kwangu kuri kumunhu here\x + 7.13. 9.27. 10.1. 23.2.\x*? Zvino kana \add zvakadaro\add*, sei moyo wangu usingapfupiswi\x + 15.13.\x*?
\v 5 Nditarirei, mugoshamisika, uye muise ruoko pamuromo\x + Vato. 18.19.\x*.
\v 6 Hongu, pandinorangarira, ndinovhiringidzwa; nekudedera kunobata nyama yangu\x + 18.20.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Sei vakaipa vachirarama vave vakwegura, zvino vakure pasimba?
\v 8 Mbeu yavo inosimbiswa pamberi pavo pamwe navo, nezvizvarwa zvavo pamberi pemeso avo.
\v 9 Dzimba dzavo dzine rugare pasina kutya, uye pasina shamhu yaMwari pamusoro pavo.
\v 10 Hando yake inokwira isingakonewi; mhou yake inobereka isingasvodzi.
\v 11 Vanobudisa vanana vavo seboka \add remakwai\add*; uye vana vavo vanotamba.
\v 12 Vanosimudza \add inzwi\add* nengoma nembira; vanofara neinzwi renyere.
\v 13 Vanopedza mazuva avo muzvakanaka, uye vanoburukira muguva nekubwaira kweziso.
\v 14 Naizvozvo vanoti kuna Mwari: Ibva kwatiri, nokuti hatishuvi ruzivo rwenzira dzako.
\v 15 Wemasimbaose chii kuti timushumire? Zvino tichawanei kana tichinyengetera kwaari?
\v 16 Tarirai, zvakanaka zvavo hazvimo muruoko rwavo; zano revakaipa riri kure neni.
\p
\v 17 Kangani mwenje wevakaipa uchidzimwa\x + 18.5.\x*, uye kuparadzwa kwavo kuchiuya pamusoro pavo? Ano\add va\add*govera matambudziko pakutsamwa kwake\x + 20.29.\x*?
\v 18 Vakaita semashanga pamberi pemhepo, uye sehundi dutu remhepo rainopeperesa\x + Map. 1.4.\x*?
\v 19 Mwari anoisira\x + 15.20.\x* vana vake dambudziko rake\x + Eki. 20.5. Det. 24.16.\x*, anopa kwaari mubairo uye anoziva\x + Isa. 9.9. Eze. 25.14. Hos. 9.7.\x*.
\v 20 Meso ake achaona kuparadzwa kwake, uye achanwa zvekutsamwa kweWemasimbaose\x + Map. 60.3. 75.8. Isa. 51.17,22. Jer. 25.15. Obh. 16. Zvak. 14.10. 16.19. 19.15.\x*.
\v 21 Nokuti mufaro wake chii muimba yake shure kwake\x + 22.3. 14.21. Isa. 58.3,13. Mup. 3.22.\x*, apo uwandu hwemwedzi yake yagurwa\x + 15.20.\x*?
\p
\v 22 \add Aripo\add* achadzidzisa Mwari ruzivo here\x + Isa. 40.14. Isa. 45.9. VaRom. 11.34. 1 VaKori. 2.16.\x*, nokuti iye anotonga vari pamusoro\x + 4.18. 15.15. 25.2,3. Map. 78.69.\x*?
\v 23 Uyu anofa pasimba rake rakaperera, iye ese akagadzikana, uye ane runyararo.
\v 24 Pombi dzake dzizere nemukaka, nemongo wemapfupa ake wakanyorova\x + Zvir. 3.8. Isa. 58.11. 66.14.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino umwe anofa ane mweya unorwadza\x + 7.11. 10.1.\x*, asina kudya zvezvakanaka\x + 21.16.\x*.
\v 26 Vacharara pamwe\x + 20.11. Mup. 9.2.\x* muguruva\x + 17.16.\x*, uye honye dzichavafukidza.
\p
\v 27 Tarirai ndinoziva ndangariro dzenyu, nemazano amunondikanganisa \add nawo\add*.
\v 28 Nokuti munoti: Iripi\x + 20.6,7.\x* imba yemuchinda\x + Zvir. 14.11.\x*? Uye riripi tende renzvimbo dzekugara dzevakaipa\x + 15.34. 18.15,21. 8.22.\x*?
\v 29 Hamuna kubvunza here vanopfuura nenzira, uye hamuzivi zviratidzo zvavo here?
\v 30 Kuti wakaipa anoregerwa pazuva rekuparadzwa\x + 38.23. 33.18. Zvir. 16.4. 2 Pet. 2.9.\x*; vachauiswa nezuva rekutsamwa.
\v 31 Ndiani achazivisa nzira yake pachiso\x + Det. 7.10. Hos. 5.5. VaGar. 2.11.\x* chake? Ndiani achatsiva zvaakaita\x + Det. 7.10. Hos. 5.5. VaGar. 2.11.\x*?
\v 32 Zvakadaro iye achauiswa kuguva, uye murwi \add wake\add* ucharindwa\x + 10.19.\x*.
\v 33 Mavhinga emupata anomutapirira\x + 38.38.\x*, uye anokweva vanhu vese shure kwake; sezvo vasingaverengeki vari mberi kwake\x + VaHeb. 9.27.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino munondinyaradza sei nezvisina maturo, nokuti \add pa\add*mhinduro dzenyu kwasara manyepo?